---
title: Lemon Chicken & Chorizo Crumb with Broccolini & Roasted Potatoes
description: Inspired by simple yet stunning Spanish cooking, this dish is pure elegance. Tender chicken is showered with a crunchy topping peppered with chorizo, while broccolini and potato bask in a bed of chargrilled capsicum relish.
